OL,3,CFake designer clothing scam boss loses
OL,4,C#90 million property empire and Ferrari
OL,6,FThe mastermind behind one of the UK's
OL,7,Fbiggest ever carousel tax frauds has
OL,8,Fbeen ordered to pay back more than #90
OL,9,Fmillion.
OL,11,FArif Patel, 57, from Preston, was
OL,12,Ffound guilty of false accounting,
OL,13,Fconspiracy to cheat the public
OL,14,Frevenue, the onward sale of
OL,15,Fcounterfeit clothing and money
OL,16,Flaundering in 2023.
OL,18,FPatel and his criminal gang tried to
OL,19,Fsteal #97 million through VAT
OL,20,Frepayment claims on false exports of
OL,21,Ftextiles and mobile phones.
