OL,3,CFake designer clothing scam boss loses
OL,4,C#90 million property empire and Ferrari
OL,6,FThey also imported and sold fake
OL,7,Fclothes, which would have been worth
OL,8,F#50 million if they were real.
OL,10,FNow a judge has ruled homes owned by
OL,11,FPatel in six cities across the world,
OL,12,Falongside his Ferrari, will be sold to
OL,13,Frecoup the money.
OL,15,FPatel and his co-accused Mohamed
OL,16,FJaffar, 61, from Dubai, were found
OL,17,Fguilty as part of a joint
OL,18,Finvestigation between HMRC and
OL,19,FLancashire Police, which saw 24 other
OL,20,Fgang members jailed for a combined
OL,21,Ftotal of over 116 years.
