OL,3,CFake designer clothing scam boss loses
OL,4,C#90 million property empire and Ferrari
OL,6,FPatel used the money raised from the
OL,7,Ffraud to fund a "property empire"
OL,8,Facross Preston, London, Morocco, UAE,
OL,9,FSaudi Arabia and Turkey.
OL,11,FA judge at Chester Crown Court has now
OL,12,Fruled that more than #90 million of
OL,13,FPatel's restrained property assets
OL,14,Fshould be sold, with the money
OL,15,Freturned to fund UK public services.
