OL,3,CFake designer clothing scam boss loses
OL,4,C#90 million property empire and Ferrari
OL,6,FRichard Las, Director, Fraud
OL,7,FInvestigation Service, HMRC, said:
OL,8,F"Arif Patel lived a lavish lifestyle
OL,9,Fat the expense of the law-abiding
OL,10,Fmajority, but he will now lose the
OL,11,Fproperty empire he amassed from the
OL,12,Fproceeds of crime.
OL,14,F"Our work never stops at conviction.
OL,15,FFor the last two years we've worked
OL,16,Fwith police and CPS partners to secure
OL,17,Fone of the biggest criminal
OL,18,Fconfiscations we've ever recovered.
