OL,6,F"Tens of millions of pounds of stolen
OL,7,Fmoney will now go back to directly
OL,8,Ffund public services."
OL,10,FWhat is carousel fraud?
OL,12,FCarousel fraud is the evasion of VAT
OL,13,Fby organised crime groups.
OL,15,FGoods are purportedly sold to genuine
OL,16,Fbuyers, but in fact the whole process
OL,17,Fis controlled by the criminal, who
OL,18,Fcreates a paper trail of alleged sales
OL,19,Fand exports in order to reclaim VAT.
