OL,4,C#90 million property empire and Ferrari
OL,6,FMark Winstanley, Assistant Chief
OL,7,FConstable, Lancashire Constabulary,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Arif Patel was the head of a
OL,9,FPreston-based Organised Crime Group
OL,10,Fresponsible for causing millions of
OL,11,Fpounds worth of losses to multiple
OL,12,Fcompanies.
OL,14,F"His actions, motivated by greed
OL,15,Fdirectly impacted on the taxpayer. A
OL,16,Fmulti-agency operation involving
OL,17,FLancashire police and HMRC has worked
OL,18,Ftirelessly to bring confiscation
OL,19,Fproceedings to this point.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
