OL,3,CFake designer clothing scam boss loses
OL,4,C#90 million property empire and Ferrari
OL,6,F"The Confiscation Order granted for
OL,7,F#90 million will ensure funds are
OL,8,Freturned to the public purse thereby
OL,9,Frecovering his criminal gains.
OL,11,F"Mohammed Jaffar Ali was Arif Patel's
OL,12,Ftrusted financial enabler in Dubai and
OL,13,Fhe too has been made subject to a
OL,14,FConfiscation Order for #677,000.
OL,16,F"Lancashire Police are committed to
OL,17,Fensuring that crime doesn't pay and
OL,18,Fwill pursue every avenue to recover
OL,19,Fmonies and assets from those that seek
OL,20,Fto exploit others for their own gain."
