OL,3,CFake designer clothing scam boss loses
OL,4,C#90 million property empire and Ferrari
OL,6,FPatel ran the counterfeit clothing and
OL,7,Ffalse export operation from his
OL,8,FPreston-based business Faisaltex Ltd,
OL,9,Fwith the help of Mohamed Jaffar Ali
OL,10,Fwho also laundered the proceeds to
OL,11,Foffshore bank accounts.
OL,13,FArif Patel travelled to Dubai in 2011
OL,14,Fand failed to return, and both men
OL,15,Fwere sentenced in absence to a total
OL,16,Fof 31 years in prison.
